             indices. Decomposes the variance of a model output Y into
             orthogonal contributions from each input X_i (first-order
             effect S_i = Var(E[Y|X_i]) / Var(Y)) and from interactions
             (higher-order effects). Used as the inline citation for the
             S1 and ST estimators returned by run\_sobol\_sensitivity in
             supply\_chain\_research/phase4\_synthesis/sensitivity\_analysis.py.}
