  volume  = {181},
  number  = {2},
  pages   = {259--270},
  year    = {2010},
  doi     = {10.1016/j.cpc.2009.09.018},
  url     = {https://doi.org/10.1016/j.cpc.2009.09.018},
  note    = {Modern Saltelli sample design: defines the matrix-based
             estimator for the total-order sensitivity index ST that
             SALib's sobol module implements. Total model evaluations
             = N * (2D + 2) for D inputs and Saltelli base size N.
             Section 6 recommends N >= 1000 for stable indices --
